=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">7</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">月在中科院动物研究所获得理学博士学位，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">2008</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">10</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">-2014</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">月在美国哈佛大学细胞与分子生物学系做博士后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">2014</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">6</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">月加入青岛农业大学。主要以哺乳动物和酵母为实验对象，长期从事卵子发育、成熟、受精和早期胚胎发育研究，着重于减数分裂染色体正确分离的分子机制研究。发表</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">SCI</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">论文累计影响因子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">&gt;110</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">，被引用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">&gt;450</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">次。担任</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">Cell\r\nCycle; Current Molecular Medicine</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:en-us;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">等十几种国际期刊</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">SCI</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">杂志审稿人。曾获省部级优秀科技成果一等奖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">项，省部级自然科学二等奖</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">项。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\"><img src=\"/Editor/attached/image/20150721//20150721151018_975.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `tmresearch` VALUES ('34', '5', '写给研究生的话', '<div><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\">本实验室以每个人的兴趣点为根本，结合国家和社会发展的需要，呈发散性地进行科学实验的探索，主要包括但不仅限于受精生物学、发育生物学、细胞生物学等微观生命科学的研究。</span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\"> </span><div><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\"> </span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\"> </span><div><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\">每个人都具有提出自己idea的权利，在不违背伦理道德的情况下，只要相关的idea具有可操作性，有实际的意义，能实实在在地回答和解决一些具体的问题，那么每个人都有实现自己idea的机会。</span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\"> </span><div><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\"> </span></div>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\"> </span><div><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\">如果您是一个有想法的人，是一个对微观生命科学有兴趣的人，欢迎您加入到我的实验室，一起探索、一起感知微观生命科学研究的乐趣！<img src=\"http://irs.qau.edu.cn/Editor/plugins/emoticons/42.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://irs.qau.edu.cn/Editor/plugins/emoticons/42.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"http://irs.qau.edu.cn/Editor/plugins/emoticons/42.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></span></div>\r\n<div><br />\r\n</div>');
INSERT INTO `tmresearch` VALUES ('38', '5', '研究方向', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:2.7pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.7pt;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Wingdings;\">u</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', serif;\">&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">优质精子筛选：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">在辅助生殖领域，主要是通过精子上游法和梯度离心技术筛选活力较好的精子用以受精，但是通过这些方法筛选出来的精子并不能保证其遗传物质的完整性，因此，不能保证其后代的健康。我们将通过研究精子的趋流反应，筛选无遗传缺陷的优质精子用以受精，以达到提高辅助生殖成功率、优生优育、动物繁育能力的目的。</span><span \"=\"\"><u1:p></u1:p></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top:2.7pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.7pt;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;line-height:15.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> </span><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:2.7pt 0cm 2.7pt 21pt;text-indent:-21pt;line-height:15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Wingdings;\">u</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', serif;\">&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">胚胎体外发育：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">子宫的缺陷是造成不孕不育的重要原因，就目前的辅助生殖技术而言，除了代孕，还无法通过其他方法实现该病症人群的生育能力。我们将致力于胚胎体外发育和建立人造子宫的研究，以期将胚胎在体外进行全程发育，为子宫缺陷型的病人提供可选择的治疗方案，助力于动物的工业化、流水线生产，提高单胎动物的繁殖速度。</span><span \"=\"\"><u1:p></u1:p></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:2.7pt 0cm 2.7pt 21pt;text-indent:-21pt;line-height:15pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> </span><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin:2.7pt 0cm 2.7pt 21pt;text-indent:-21pt;line-height:15pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Wingdings;\">u</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:\'Times New Roman\', serif;\">&nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span></span><b><span \";mso-font-kerning:=\"\" \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">RNA</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">定位研究：</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">以</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Hela</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">细胞为例，一个典型的人类细胞含有约</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">12000</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">种</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">mRNA</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">，而其中的</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">11000</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">多种在每个细胞中的丰度非常低，仅含有</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">5~15</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">拷贝。因此，大部分</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">RNA</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">在细胞中必须具有严格的定位才能实现其功能。研究</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">RNA</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">的定位有助于明确基因表达的调控方式，探明细胞和个体的衰老本质，从而达到预防和治疗疾病的目的。本研究组将致力于</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">RNA</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">定位的研究，主要包括</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">RNA</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">怎样定位，定位于细胞中的哪些细胞器，不同的</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">RNA</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">具有哪些定位特征，</span><span \"=\"\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">RNA</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">由细胞核到细胞质通过哪些机制实现其定位。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:6.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> </span><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"> </span><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>');
INSERT INTO `tmresearch` VALUES ('39', '5', '实验室成员', '<p style=\"margin-top:2.7pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.7pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:9.65pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\">PI</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\">：罗世明<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\"> </span><p style=\"margin:2.7pt 0cm;line-height:9.65pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:9pt;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.7pt 0cm;line-height:9.65pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:KaiTi_GB2312;\">在读研究生：孙小红 崔倩 范晓燕<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');
INSERT INTO `tmresearch` VALUES ('42', '7', '研究方向', '<p><b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">1，卵母细胞表观遗传的人为修饰以及其对卵母细胞的影响</span></b></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （1）改变卵母细胞的特定区域的DNA甲基化修饰，并使之传递到子代。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:10px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （2）对卵母细胞的基因组印迹进行人为修饰，研究基因组印迹对卵母细胞和胚胎发育的作用。</span></p>\r\n<p><b><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">2，卵母细胞与早期胚胎的DNA双链损伤</span></b></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （1）研究卵母细胞与早期胚胎应对DNA损伤的机制。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （2）通过DNA损伤，研究卵母细胞减数分裂与染色体进化。</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><b>3，生殖细胞代谢组学研究</b></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （1）生殖细胞的代谢重编程，以及不同代谢物对卵母细胞和早期胚胎发育的影响。</p>');
INSERT INTO `tmresearch` VALUES ('43', '9', '研究方向', '<p style=\"margin-top:2.35pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.35pt;margin-left:0cm;mso-line-height-alt:8.45pt;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、减数分裂染色体正确分离的分子机制</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）同源染色体配对重组，</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）姐妹染色单体同向定向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）姐妹染色单体着丝粒黏附连接的保护</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span>）纺锤体检验点蛋白</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;line-height:8.45pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、卵母细胞的成熟</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></b><span class=\"apple-converted-space\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:7.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:7.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）卵母细胞减数分裂的启动</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）卵母细胞中的<span lang=\"EN-US\">RNA</span>修饰</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;line-height:8.45pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.5pt;font-family:Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin:2.35pt 0cm;\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、生殖健康与生殖力<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:2.35pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.35pt;margin-left:0cm;mso-line-height-alt:8.45pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）环境对生殖健康的影响<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:2.35pt;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:2.35pt;margin-left:0cm;mso-line-height-alt:8.45pt;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）提高动物繁殖力的产品开发<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');
